        future: "By withstanding the coming challenges, your future will be bright. Seeing things as you want them to be in order to make them become that way. Knowing the worst is behind you can give strength.",
        yes_no: "The Tower is all about unexpected events and changes coming up in your life. However, the changes are along the lines of something catastrophic, disastrous, and overall negative. It could be related to some sort of accident, disaster, or damage to another area of your life. The answer provided by this card is no.",
        numerology: "16",
